## Request for Victim Support Preparation

As this situation may soon receive media coverage, there is a high likelihood that victims of sexual violence at Dongguk University and other Korean institutions may come forward. We therefore request the following preparations:

1. Verification of support service availability, particularly for arts department students
2. Preparation of multilingual support services for international students
3. Enhancement of anonymous reporting mechanisms
4. Development of strategies to minimize secondary victimization

